                                <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:8.0pt;margin-left:0cm;font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Aptos",sans-serif;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;'><span style='font-size:16px;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;color:#555555;'>En resumen: recopilamos los registros de stock que usted registra en el aplicativo.&nbsp;</span></p>
                                <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:8.0pt;margin-left:0cm;font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Aptos",sans-serif;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;'><strong><span style='font-size:24px;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;color:#333333;'>Informaci&oacute;n recopilada autom&aacute;ticamente</span></strong></p>
